Z/z: Roll counterclockwise/clockwise in the xy-coordinate plane.
X/x: Pitch up/down
C/c: Yaw counterclockwsise/clockwise in the zx-coordinate plane
Left/Right Arrow:  Moves camera left and right
Up/Down Arrow - Moves camera up and down. 
Q/q: Moves camera forwards and backwards.
w: Moves look at vector up.
a: Moves look at vector left.
s: Moves look at vector down.
d: Moves look at vector right.

t: Set cube materials to bricks.
T: Set cube materials to crate.

Spacebar: Turns flashlight on (off by default).
m: Turns flashlight off

u: toggles animation

O/o : toggles camera
